description:
Which? has volunteered to host a talks session at its 4th floor office at One Castle Park (supplying the obligatory beer and pizza)

The schedule of talks:

Using Django as a stop gap network automation solution - Ed Crewe

AIML: What is AI? - Chloe Parkes

Integrating ReactJS with Django  -  Murat Sert

Creating and publishing your first python library - Dale Potter
title: Talks session at Which? Office - One Castle Park
